---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTA from '../components/CTA.astro';
import { business } from '../data/business';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Pet Health Info Center | Healthy Paws Animal Hospital"
  description="Educational pet health resources from Healthy Paws Animal Hospital. Guides for new pet owners, preventive care, senior pets, nutrition, and emergencies in Lake in the Hills, IL."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="bg-hpah-green-light py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="text-hpah-green font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Pet Health Info Center</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl mb-6">The Gift of Education Keeps on Giving</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-hpah-text-light">
        At Healthy Paws, we believe informed pet owners make the best decisions for their animals.
        This resource center is designed to help you understand your pet's health needs at every stage of life.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Resource Sections -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="container max-w-5xl">

      <!-- New Pet Owners -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-hpah-green-light rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-hpah-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl">New Pet Owners</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-hpah-text-light mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Bringing home a new puppy, kitten, or adopted pet is exciting — and comes with a lot of questions. These
          resources will help you start off on the right foot with a solid foundation of preventive care, proper
          nutrition, and an understanding of what to expect during your first year together.
        </p>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <a href="/your-first-visit/" class="block bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-hpah-green transition-colors">
            <p class="font-semibold text-hpah-text">Your First Visit</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light mt-1">What to expect and how to prepare</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/pet-vaccinations-lake-in-the-hills-il/" class="block bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-hpah-green transition-colors">
            <p class="font-semibold text-hpah-text">Vaccination Schedules</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light mt-1">Core and lifestyle vaccines for puppies and kittens</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/spay-neuter-lake-in-the-hills-il/" class="block bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-hpah-green transition-colors">
            <p class="font-semibold text-hpah-text">Spay & Neuter</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light mt-1">Timing, benefits, and what to expect</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/microchipping/" class="block bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-hpah-green transition-colors">
            <p class="font-semibold text-hpah-text">Microchipping</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light mt-1">Permanent identification for your pet's safety</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Preventive Care -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-hpah-green-light rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-hpah-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl">Preventive Care</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-hpah-text-light mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Prevention is always more effective — and less expensive — than treatment. Regular wellness exams, dental
          care, and parasite prevention are the foundation of a long, healthy life for your pet. Our preventive care
          approach catches problems early, when they're easiest to address.
        </p>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <a href="/wellness-exams-lake-in-the-hills-il/" class="block bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-hpah-green transition-colors">
            <p class="font-semibold text-hpah-text">Wellness Exams</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light mt-1">Comprehensive annual and semi-annual checkups</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/dental-care/" class="block bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-hpah-green transition-colors">
            <p class="font-semibold text-hpah-text">Dental Care</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light mt-1">Professional cleanings, home care tips, and dental health</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/pet-vaccinations-lake-in-the-hills-il/" class="block bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-hpah-green transition-colors">
            <p class="font-semibold text-hpah-text">Vaccinations</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light mt-1">Tailored vaccine protocols based on lifestyle risk</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/laboratory-diagnostics/" class="block bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-hpah-green transition-colors">
            <p class="font-semibold text-hpah-text">Lab & Diagnostics</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light mt-1">Bloodwork, urinalysis, and early disease screening</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Senior Pet Care -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-hpah-green-light rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-hpah-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl">Senior Pet Care</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-hpah-text-light mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Aging pets have unique health needs. Dogs are generally considered senior at age 7, and cats around age 11.
          Regular wellness checks become even more important as your pet ages, helping us detect and manage conditions
          like arthritis, kidney disease, diabetes, and cognitive changes early.
        </p>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <a href="/senior-pet-care-lake-in-the-hills-il/" class="block bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-hpah-green transition-colors">
            <p class="font-semibold text-hpah-text">Senior Pet Care</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light mt-1">Specialized care for aging dogs and cats</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/pain-management/" class="block bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-hpah-green transition-colors">
            <p class="font-semibold text-hpah-text">Pain Management</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light mt-1">Keeping your senior pet comfortable and active</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/nutrition-counseling/" class="block bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-hpah-green transition-colors">
            <p class="font-semibold text-hpah-text">Senior Nutrition</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light mt-1">Diet adjustments for aging bodies</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/end-of-life-care/" class="block bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-hpah-green transition-colors">
            <p class="font-semibold text-hpah-text">End of Life Care</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light mt-1">Compassionate guidance when the time comes</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Emergency Info -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl">Emergency Information</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-hpah-text-light mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Knowing what constitutes a veterinary emergency — and what to do when one happens — can save your pet's life.
          We provide same-day urgent care during business hours. For after-hours emergencies, we'll direct you to the
          nearest 24-hour emergency facility.
        </p>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <a href="/emergency-urgent-care/" class="block bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-hpah-green transition-colors">
            <p class="font-semibold text-hpah-text">Emergency & Urgent Care</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light mt-1">When to seek immediate help</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/specialty-partners/" class="block bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-hpah-green transition-colors">
            <p class="font-semibold text-hpah-text">Specialty & Referral Partners</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light mt-1">When your pet needs advanced care</p>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 bg-red-50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-red-100">
          <p class="font-semibold text-red-800 mb-2">If your pet is experiencing an emergency:</p>
          <p class="text-red-700">
            Call us immediately at <a href={`tel:${business.phoneRaw}`} class="font-bold underline">{business.phone}</a> during business hours.
            If we're closed, contact your nearest 24-hour emergency veterinary hospital.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Nutrition -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-hpah-green-light rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-hpah-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 3h2l.4 2M7 13h10l4-8H5.4M7 13L5.4 5M7 13l-2.293 2.293c-.63.63-.184 1.707.707 1.707H17m0 0a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4zm-8 2a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl">Nutrition & Diet</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-hpah-text-light mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          What your pet eats directly impacts their health, energy, weight, and longevity. With hundreds of pet food
          brands making competing claims, choosing the right diet can feel overwhelming. Our veterinarians provide
          evidence-based nutrition guidance tailored to your pet's specific needs — not influenced by any brand partnerships.
        </p>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <a href="/nutrition-counseling/" class="block bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-hpah-green transition-colors">
            <p class="font-semibold text-hpah-text">Nutrition Counseling</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light mt-1">Personalized diet recommendations</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/pet-allergy-treatment-lake-in-the-hills-il/" class="block bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-hpah-green transition-colors">
            <p class="font-semibold text-hpah-text">Food Allergies</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-hpah-text-light mt-1">Identifying and managing dietary sensitivities</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Blog Callout -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-hpah-bg-warm">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl mb-4">Visit Our Blog</h2>
      <p class="text-hpah-text-light mb-6">
        Our blog features seasonal health tips, in-depth articles on common pet health topics, and updates from
        our team. It's another way we live our education-first philosophy — sharing knowledge beyond the exam room.
      </p>
      <a href="/blog/" class="btn-primary">Read Our Blog</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTA heading="Have a Health Question?" text="Our team is always happy to answer your questions — whether you're a current patient or considering Healthy Paws for the first time." />
</BaseLayout>
